[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps - Classic Pits[/b]
Week 6 of 12 - 2018 Season 1 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]9 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]2:50.197[/b] by Ronny Dudeck
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

Week 6 takes us to the historic Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps, affectionately known just as "Spa". This long track makes for epic draft battles with the SRF. Strategy will be key to good results here - time your attacks carefully and plan for a close finish!

[color=red][b]N.B. due to the length of the lap there is only time for ONE qualifying lap. As the offtracks are very tight here it's recommended to be careful to post a valid time![/b][/color]

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

